measurements.description:
An island of display at the show entrance, plants grown by many members of the San Francisco Orchid 
	 Society, comprised of a wide variety of orchid genera; large, well-grown specimen size cymbidiums 
	 and dendrobiums were the focal point of the display, surrounded by paphiopedilums, phragmipediums, 
	 cattleyas, rossioglossums, and may other genera, against a backdrop of a pine tree, with white phalaenopsis
	 placed throughout the display to draw the eye from point to point; a unicorn and a tall mushroom with a giant dragon fly showcased the theme of the show: 
	 Orchids of the Enchanted Forest.
